 />\n咁三個月後你可唔可以原諒黑警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以時間長唔等於可以原諒，無必然關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鍾意睇咪會睇囉，講咩原唔原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前鍾意睇達哥，係因為佢嘅人生態度，<br />\n教人做人處事方式，令我認同佢係一個君子，<br />\n但你叫我而家點睇返佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果為左利益，我可以明白，甚至接受，因為我知達哥一定係企我地呢邊，雨傘已經知道。咁你一直唔岀聲咪算囉，做咩無端端要屌人，又講到自己忍辱負重咁，敢做唔敢認呢下真係好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都算！我扮睇唔到！屌你下個post係派糖抽獎...... 到底你當你d fans係咩人.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個status我希望係佢公關團隊自把自為要岀，我希望我以前唔係一直睇緊個假人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecc2c399225729e9786d405d00e935372444f29","tid":1554921,"uid":219369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"达狗不了"},{"pid":"c7470dd2db3b255b44669c042adb0c03d4978e65","tid":1554921,"uid":5605,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"我地 都係 一班<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爆機兄弟！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"42d456c02b04dd539003781059dbe937e40a6646","tid":1554921,"uid":250206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"警太都有一直關注件事架，都過咗3個月啦，點解你又唔原諒佢地？"},{"pid":"f56e8c49c0b67f9baaf92833710cc35b21856119","tid":1554921,"uid":250206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42d456c02b04dd539003781059dbe937e40a6646","tid":1554921,"uid":250206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"警太都有一直關注件事架，都過咗3個月啦，點解你又唔原諒佢地？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"警犬*"},{"pid":"537c8a48750a52637ae6761f1389ee94b0597a0b","tid":1554921,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:52:00.000Z","msg":"<span sty